2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1618811339","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1618811339","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":172520,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1618811339","stars":3230,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"username":"lrs","website":null,"github":null,"psn":null,"avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/246ef4a1dc6acc92c8297c99e873064c?s=24&d=retro","bio":null,"url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/lrs","tagline":null,"twitter":null,"created":1619226270,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/246ef4a1dc6acc92c8297c99e873064c?s=24&d=retro","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/246ef4a1dc6acc92c8297c99e873064c?s=24&d=retro","location":null,"btc":null,"id":543517},"last_reply_by":"Tianao","last_touched":1621398583,"title":"QUIC 协议基于 UDP， UDP 不可靠， QUIC 如何保证可靠性的呢","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/777845","created":1621392014,"content":"最近写代码练手，写一个网络发送文件的小程序，可选 TCP 或 UDP 为传输方案。写到 UDP 传输方案的时候发现丢包检测重传之类的逻辑越写越乱越写越复杂，于是准备看下 QUIC 怎么实现的。翻了翻 QUIC 的 RFC 文档，看的我头大。\r\n比较好奇的是，既然 UDP 会丢包，包含传输控制信息的包也是会丢的。控制信息要是丢了，岂不就是 hang 在那里了啊。如果采用超时机制来保证控制信息的重传，这效率（传输速度）就没法保证了。\r\n所以，QUIC 是如何做的呢","content_rendered":"最近写代码练手，写一个网络发送文件的小程序，可选 TCP 或 UDP 为传输方案。写到 UDP 传输方案的时候发现丢包检测重传之类的逻辑越写越乱越写越复杂，于是准备看下 QUIC 怎么实现的。翻了翻 QUIC 的 RFC 文档，看的我头大。<br />比较好奇的是，既然 UDP 会丢包，包含传输控制信息的包也是会丢的。控制信息要是丢了，岂不就是 hang 在那里了啊。如果采用超时机制来保证控制信息的重传，这效率（传输速度）就没法保证了。<br />所以，QUIC 是如何做的呢","last_modified":1621392014,"replies":17,"id":777845},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_large.png?m=1583044904","name":"windows","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_normal.png?m=1583044904","title":"Windows","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/windows","topics":2021,"footer":"","header":"Windows, not walls.","title_alternative":"Windows